msgid "Cuts blocks of granite and marble out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr "Hakt blokken graniet en marmer uit rotsen in de omgeving."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Frisian worker: Stonemason
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2590 input:2590
#: standard
