msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The lumberjack’s hut needs trees to fell within the work area."
msgstr ""
"De houthakkershut heeft bomen nodig om te kappen binnen het werkgebied."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Woodcutters House
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4537 input:4537
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The lumberjack’s house needs trees to fell within the work area."
msgstr ""
"Het houthakkershuis heeft bomen nodig om te kappen binnen het werkgebied."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Liana Cutter's Hut
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4544 input:4544
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Home of the liana cutter who cuts lianas for making ropes."
msgstr ""
"Woonplaats van de lianensnijder die lianen snijdt voor het maken van touwen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Liana Cutter's Hut
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4546 input:4546
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The liana cutter harvests liana from fully matured trees within the work "
"area which are not being used as lookouts."
msgstr ""
"De lianensnijder oogst lianen van volledig volgroeide bomen binnen het "
"werkgebied die niet als uitkijkposten worden gebruikt."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Rare Tree Cutter's Hut
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4553 input:4553
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Harvests rare trees in the surrounding area. Delivers ironwood, balsa and "
"rubber."
msgstr ""
"Oogst zeldzame bomen in de omgeving. Levert ijzerhout, balsahout en rubber."

