#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Clay Pit
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4668 input:4668
#: standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid ""
"Digs up mud from the ground and uses water to turn it into clay. Clay is "
"used to make bricks, reinforce the charcoal kiln and to build ships."
msgstr ""
"Graaft modder uit de grond en gebruikt water om er klei van te maken. Klei "
"wordt gebruikt om bakstenen te maken, de houtskooloven te versterken en "
"schepen te bouwen."

