#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:6090 input:6076
#: input:6090 standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Ballad ‘The Battle of Kal’mavrath’ by Hakhor the Bard"
msgstr "Ballade ‘De Slag bij Kal'mavrath’ door Hakhor de Bard"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Barbarian military site: Tower
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:6088 input:6088
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"‘From the height of our tower we could see far into enemy territory. The "
"enemy was well prepared, but we also noticed some weak points in their "
"defense.’"
msgstr ""
"‘Vanaf de top van onze toren konden we ver het vijandelijke gebied in "
"kijken. De vijand was goed voorbereid, maar we zagen ook enkele zwakke "
"punten in hun verdediging.’"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Barbarian military site: Fortress
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:6101 input:6101
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"‘This stronghold made from blackwood and stones will be a hard nut to crack "
"for them.’"
msgstr ""
"'Deze vesting van rozenhout en stenen zal voor hen een harde noot om te "
"kraken zijn.'"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Barbarian military site: Fortress
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:6103 input:6103
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Berthron,<br>chief military adviser of Chat’Karuth"
msgstr "Berthron,<br>militair hoofdadviseur van Chat'Karuth"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Barbarian military site: Citadel
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:6114 input:6114
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"‘The Citadel of Adlen surely is the finest masterpiece of Barbarian "
"craftsmanship. Nothing as strong and big and beautiful has ever been built "
"in such a short time.’"
msgstr ""
"'De Citadel van Adlen is zonder twijfel het mooiste meesterwerk van de "
"barbaarse bouwkunst. Nooit eerder is er in zo'n korte tijd iets gebouwd dat "
"zo sterk, groot en mooi is.'"

